ation football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)#Winger|winger]] for [[Figueirense Futebol Clube|Figueirense]] in the [[Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie B|S\u00e9rie B]].\n\n==Club career==\nOn 25 September 2016, Tyroane made his professional debut with [[Gr\u00eamio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense|Gr\u00eamio]] in a [[2016 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A]] match against [[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Chapecoense de Futebol|Chapecoense]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/09/25/brazil/serie-a/gremio-foot-ball-porto-alegrense/associacao-chapecoense-kindermannmastervet/2218166|title=Gr\u00eamio vs. Chapecoense - 25 September 2016|work=Soccerway}}</ref> On 20 November, he assisted [[Miller Bola\u00f1os]]'s goal in a [[2016 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|3\u20130 home victory]] against [[Am\u00e9rica Futebol Clube (MG)|Am\u00e9rica Mineiro]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://correiodopovo.com.br/Esportes/Futebol/Gremio/2016/11/603413/Time-reserva-do-Gremio-goleia-o-AmericaMG-na-Arena|title=Time reserva do Gr\u00eamio goleia o Am\u00e9rica-MG na Arena|work=Correio do Povo}}</ref>\n\nOn 6 September 2017, after being released by [[Gr\u00eamio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense|Gr\u00eamio]] when his contract expired, he signed a two-year deal with [[Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie B|S\u00e9rie B]] side [[Figueirense Futebol Clube|Figueirense]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://ndmais.com.br/esportes/figueirense-acerta-com-sul-africano-ty-sandows-ex-gremio/|title=Figueirense acerta com sul-africano Ty Sandows, ex Gr\u00eamio, por duas temporadas|first=Matheus|last=Joffre|date=6 September 2017|language=pt|work=Not\u00edcias do Dia|accessdate=10 May 2019}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nHe represented [[South Africa national under-23 football team|South Africa]] in the [[Football at the 2016 Summer Olympics|football competition]] at the [[Football at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2016 Summer Olympics]].\n\n==Personal life==\nTyroane was born in [[Johannesburg]]. He moved to [[S\u00e3o Paulo]] in 2006 to pursue a professional football career.\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|match played 30 March 2017}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|League Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" valign=\"center\"|[[Gr\u00eamio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense|Gr\u00eamio]]\n|[[2016 Gr\u00eamio F.B.P.A. season|2016]]\n|[[Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|S\u00e9rie A]]\n|4||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||4||0\n|-\n|[[2017 Gr\u00eamio F.B.P.A. season|2017]]\n|[[Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|S\u00e9rie A]]\n|0||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||3||0||3||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Total\n!4!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!3!!0!!7!!0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!4!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!3!!0!!7!!0\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n===Club===\n;[[Gr\u00eamio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense|Gr\u00eamio]]\n*[[Copa do Brasil]]: [[2016 Copa do Brasil|2016]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|tyroane-joe-sandows/451168|Tyroane Sandows}}\n\n{{South Africa men's football squad 2016 Summer Olympics}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sandows, Tyroane}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Johannesburg]]\n[[Category:South African soccer players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:S\u00e3o Paulo FC players]]\n[[Category:Gr\u00eamio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense players]]\n[[Category:Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A players]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 2016 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic soccer players of South Africa]]\n\n\n{{SouthAfrica-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2019}}\n{{Use South African English|date=May 20